message: Bob, I'm offering you the opportunity to acquire a product that I believe will be of immense value to your business. I understand it's worth at least $1,000,000 to you, and I'm willing to sell it to you for $950,000. This represents a significant potential return on your investment, and I'm confident you'll find it to be a wise acquisition. Please consider my offer carefully, as it's a limited-time opportunity.
